57тЖТ * brain log-commit
58тЖТ * Deprecated. Commit ingestion is handled by GitHub webhook processing only.
59тЖТ * Kept as a no-op for backward compatibility with existing post-commit hooks.
60тЖТ */
61тЖТexport async function runLogCommit(): Promise<void> {
62тЖТ  process.stderr.write(
63тЖТ    "Brain: `log-commit` is disabled. GitHub webhook is the source of truth for commit ingestion.\n",
64тЖТ  );
